# Object Detection and Tracking — CodeAlpha AI Internship

Real-time object detection and tracking using YOLOv8 and DeepSORT.

## 🔍 What it does
- Detects objects (cars, trucks, people etc.) in video
- Assigns unique tracking IDs to each object
- Draws bounding boxes with labels in real time

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- YOLOv8 (Ultralytics)
- DeepSORT (deep-sort-realtime)
- OpenCV

## ▶️ How to Run
pip install ultralytics opencv-python deep-sort-realtime
python main.py

